Date:   Sat Dec 28 09:21:22 2024 +0000

    [VectorCombine] foldShuffleOfBinops - only accept exact matching cmp
predicates

    m_SpecificCmp allowed equivalent predicate+flags which don't necessarily
work after being folded from "shuffle (cmpop), (cmpop)" into "cmpop (shuffle),
(shuffle)"

    Fixes #121110

