vector-combine pass is incorrectly transforming a shuffle of two different
comparison operations (one with 'samesign ugt' and another with 'sgt') into a
single comparison operation. The source IR produces <i1 false, i1 true> but the
transformed IR produces <i1 false, i1 false>, which is incorrect.\n\n2.
