two comparison operations have different predicates - one is 'samesign ugt' and
the other is 'sgt'.\n\n3. Root Cause Analysis: In the `foldShuffleOfBinops`
function, the code matches both LHS and RHS as comparison operations
using:\n```cpp\nmatch(LHS, m_Cmp(Pred, m_Value(X), m_Value(Y))) &&\nmatch(RHS,
